@startuml UC3_BorrowDevice

title UC3 - Borrow Device (Simple Sequence)

actor User
participant UI
participant System
database Database

User -> UI : Click Borrow button
UI -> User : Show quantity selection popup
User -> UI : Confirm borrow
UI -> System : Send borrow request
System -> Database : Update device quantity
Database --> System : Update success
System --> UI : Borrow success response
UI --> User : Show confirmation

@enduml
